---
// Componente Gerente - Sección del Gerente General
---

<section class="gerente-section">
  <div class="gerente-container">
    <div class="gerente-profile">
      <div class="gerente-image-container">
        <img
          src="/images/gerente.webp"
          alt="David Álvarez - CEO y Gerente General"
          class="gerente-image"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="gerente-info">
        <h3 class="gerente-name">David Álvarez</h3>
        <p class="gerente-title">CEO y gerente general</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gerente-divider"></div>
    <div class="gerente-quote">
      <h4 class="gerente-quote-title">Frase gerente general</h4>
      <blockquote class="gerente-quote-text">
        Automatiza procesos en Microsoft 365, protege tu información con Acronis
        y transforma tu forma de trabajar con Inteligencia Artificial.
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Estilos para la sección del Gerente */
  .gerente-section {
    background: #010738 !important;
    padding: 4rem 2rem !important;
    color: white !important;
    width: 100% !important;
    display: block !important;
  }

  .gerente-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem 15rem;
  }

  .gerente-profile {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  .gerente-image-container {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .gerente-image {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .gerente-info {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .gerente-name {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: white;
  }

  .gerente-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: white;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .gerente-divider {
    width: 2px;
    height: 120px;
    background: white;
    margin: 0 2rem;
  }

  .gerente-quote {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .gerente-quote-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    color: white;
  }

  .gerente-quote-text {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .gerente-quote-text::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #fa4517;
    position: absolute;
    left: 32px;
    top: -1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .gerente-quote-text::after {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #fa4517;
    position: absolute;
    right: 3rem;
    bottom: 0rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .gerente-section {
      padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .gerente-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .gerente-divider {
      width: 80%;
      height: 2px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .gerente-quote-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .gerente-quote-text {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }

    .gerente-quote-text::before {
      font-size: 3rem;
      top: -0.5rem;
    }

    .gerente-quote-text::after {
      font-size: 3rem;
      right: -1rem;
      bottom: -1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .gerente-section {
      padding: 2rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .gerente-container {
      gap: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 0.5rem;
    }

    .gerente-image-container {
      width: 140px;
      height: 140px;
    }

    .gerente-image {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
    }

    .gerente-name {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .gerente-title {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .gerente-quote-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .gerente-quote-text {
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
    }

    .gerente-quote-text::before {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      top: -0.3rem;
    }

    .gerente-quote-text::after {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      right: -0.5rem;
      bottom: -1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
